{
  "stem": "10406.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when my father comes, you're going to go back with him to the other village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then a week later, he's going to come back and bring you back here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this way, it'll be as though his father found the boy pasturing the cows and brought him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's exactly what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I came back when his father came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he took me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a week later, he brought me back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I stayed there till the summer of '43.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the summer of '43, the Ukrainian population in that area, who were the majority, decided that the Polish Catholics in that area, who were a small minority, who needs them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we get rid of them, we can get their farms and stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they started-- organized attacks on the Polish villages or colonies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was getting pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somehow, the family that I lived with got word that they'll probably attack this particular area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they decided to-- to run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they packed up the wagon with all their-- whatever they could take.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they ran to my town, to Maciejow, for German protection, to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now, I had a choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Either I go with them or I stay here and get killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I went with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when we arrived in the town, the German Gestapo were there and were standing near the church property.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were directing everybody in there to stay there for the time being.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, one of the girls that came from our village had a relative in town or a friend.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Comes back with this little boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I saw the little boy, I saw trouble.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The little boy looks at me, looks at me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
